ðŸ§  Interpretation

The model performs well at identifying No Drought conditions (high precision), but struggles with Drought due to class imbalance.

SMOTE was used to synthetically balance the training data, helping improve detection of the minority "Drought" class.

Lower precision and recall for drought indicates room for improvementâ€”this could be addressed by tuning the threshold further, collecting more data, or using different algorithms.
